    "bio_summary": "Azekel Adesuyi, is a Nigerian born British singer-songwriter, musician and producer from East London.\n\nHe debuted in February 2013 with That Feeling and A Song to an Unborn Child (Delilah) produced by Nexphase of Tastemaker Music.\nA five track EP, the \"Circa EP\", was released digitally in October via Thunderlightning Recordings. \"Raw, Vol. 1\" followed on June 2015. It includes the lead singles New Romance , Mad about the boy and Chronophobia. A further track, The War Inside, rounded-up the year.",
